Cloud, huh... Somehow I find it hard to identify with Cloud... that or I'm just not his biggest fan. Not sure why I can't be Tifa but I'll take comfort in knowing that if I had answered "Gun and Claw" instead of "Longsword" when I chose my weapon, I would have been Vincent. Because, you know, its kind of cool to be Sephiroth's daddy. :-P <--- The very image of apathy

But sometimes I wonder if its really worth playing anymore. The game itself is a lot of fun but the people hoave gotten so immature. Some of them are being outright mean. I absolutely hate one of the leaders of a guild we ally with for Molten Core and I'm seriously considering never raiding with them again after I get my last two set pieces. I don't want to cause drama and I don't have screen shots or anything I can prove this with, so I'm thinking I'll just save the $15 a month. My account expires sometime in December. I'll have to look into that. There's no particular reason for me to renew it right away anyway.

...because sometimes I just need somewhere to post random frustrated comments. Too bad I don't know someone with a Dead Journal. It would be so much more appropriate. This just seems so emo....

I have a rose tinted brain, somewhere.
Here it is! I've created a LiveJournal. I'm not really sure why... I think because CelticAngel140 has one.
